無人落charge \n無警停職\n\n無忘721\n記者請日日問</code></pre>"},{"pid":"3aa77b3487f4754f8548fdf017ad976a00abbd44","tid":1442673,"uid":41458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T04:37:26.000Z","msg":"721 元朗恐襲 警黑勾結"},{"pid":"649e6164dd313d61a20eb978dd2c2a5ec4103318","tid":1442673,"uid":101625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T04:37:31.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"69f40338f53092451127dc9488c4a411dbc872a4","tid":1442673,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T04:37:32.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">針對警方無差別襲擊，標籤為<span style=\"color: red;\">國家恐怖主義武裝組織</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">文宣核彈 - 為恐怖主義正名</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qMJqUur.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqMJqUur.jpg&h=36fb98e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n恐怖主義標籤係諸國用嚟打壓異己嘅手法，「國家當局可用以將政敵或其他對手非法化，從而使國家武裝部隊可理直氣壯地打擊敵人」，包括支那對新疆嘅打壓，都係以打擊恐怖主義為名，效果顯著。若果我地為警隊嘅恐怖主義正名，絕對係致命打擊警隊嘅合法性同認受性嘅方法。<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">佢標籤我地做港獨，我地標籤返佢做「國家恐怖主義份子」 正名標籤警方為非法嘅武裝組織</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1426058\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1426058</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">無差別襲擊製造恐怖氣氛絕對已經係恐怖主義！我地係嘅係要為警隊嘅行為正名！</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">警隊失控無差別襲擊，係屬於國家恐怖主義嘅行為，已經超越「過度暴力」、「濫捕」同「濫用暴力」，依啲字眼淡化佢嘅「拐帶」、「恐怖襲擊」等非法行為，警隊嘅行為喺好多國家已經係可以定義為失去合法性啲武裝組織。<br />\n而且加上721恐襲同打後嘅黑警合作，有理由相信依個恐怖主義組織係跨越明同暗。現時警察喺民間嘅認受性極低，執法行動已變質，失去合法地執行職務嘅能力，街坊見到警察嘅武裝會產生恐懼感。恐怖主義管治已引起社會及國際極度不安。</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fool1-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/fr/cp0/e15/q65/67630995_110432746967840_2331413204384612352_o.jpg?_nc_cat=107&amp;efg=eyJpIjoidCJ9&amp;_nc_oc=AQl4L1bx4RYkXXmGjLvLvV0mieI9WjtsALdVP9McHQyfw-djgsY6ZSsf-1vl88RayEY&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fool1-1.fna&amp;oh=58b06b4db0bdb4fb6b665e75af38d026&amp;oe=5DD55B02\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fool1-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2Ffr%2Fcp0%2Fe15%2Fq65%2F67630995_110432746967840_2331413204384612352_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D107%26efg%3DeyJpIjoidCJ9%26_nc_oc%3DAQl4L1bx4RYkXXmGjLvLvV0mieI9WjtsALdVP9McHQyfw-djgsY6ZSsf-1vl88RayEY%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fool1-1.fna%26oh%3D58b06b4db0bdb4fb6b665e75af38d026%26oe%3D5DD55B02&h=2d15fa1a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">無差別化武襲擊！！</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">[過期催淚彈][有圖] 毒到連眼都起水泡！！！！！麻煩全世界前線中線後線街坊啊婆啊伯！！戴靚少少既Gear唔該！！！！！</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1436725\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1436725</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">認同請聯署請分享</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/officially-recognize-hong-kong-police-force-hkpf-led-commissioner-stephen-lo-wai-chung-terrorist-organization\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fofficially-recognize-hong-kong-police-force-hkpf-led-commissioner-stephen-lo-wai-chung-terrorist-organization&d=haqyWHVU0l66G8glzozbUyPhHSzXeBMEaaQhzK3ZYsY%3D&h=168838e0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/officially-recognize-hong-kong-police-force-hkpf-led-commissioner-stephen-lo-wai-chung-terrorist-organization</a><br />\n已有<span style=\"color: orange;\">45,938</span>/100,000個簽名（11 Aug 2019 at 12:37）<br />\n［白宮聯署］香港警察為恐怖組織<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1427701\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1427701</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">警黑合作 恐怖治國<br />\n警察本色 恐怖組織</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">槍炮化武 無差別襲擊<br />\n警黑勾結 武裝巴結<br />\nHKPF IS STATE TERRORIST!<br />\nNO STATE TERRORISM!<br />\nNO INDISCRIMINATE ATTACK!</span></span><br />\n<br />\n821守衛香港 反警黑恐怖治國 反恐大遊行/集會（未定）<br />\n821 - 元朗恐襲紀念日<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1442294\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1442294</a>"},{"pid":"af6288a244b275b7c4d9cd1da0a3aa1a73e84cf1","tid":1442673,"uid":263419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T04:37:39.000Z","msg":"<pre><code data-type=\"\">#argue#pig#argue#pig</code></pre>"},{"pid":"cd7b5339b11c6bf6438229056454c75ff846b790","tid":1442673,"uid":272422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T04:38:52.000Z","msg":"推 勿忘官警鄉黑勾結 追究元朗恐怖襲擊"},{"pid":"08d3b079678ade2c903f5f48409ec852a0aa2201","tid":1442673,"uid":245371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T04:38:55.000Z","msg":"小心誤變成連登蠕蟲及幫兇<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dAEcdS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dAEcdS</a><br />\n幫推<br />\n睇下內容, 集中推1個post thanks."},{"pid":"4ad2df2d63a6f24d1b0124a0b58fa53366478eec","tid":1442673,"uid":89006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T04:39:26.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"8fc266b50c16a3d95f20267f9b83375ffa01ec9a","tid":1442673,"uid":1616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T04:40:20.000Z","msg":"721 721"}]}